org.hps.record.epics

Class EpicsGenericObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hps.record.epics.EpicsGenericObject
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GenericObject

    final class EpicsGenericObject
extends Object
implements GenericObject
    This is an implementation of GenericObject for reading and writing EPICS data. There is no functionality here intended for ends users. Instead, the EPICS data should be accessed using EpicsData.read(org.lcsim.event.EventHeader) to create the data object from input event data.
